      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">Competitive Scrabble has produced legends whose mental abilities rival any intellectual sport. From photographic memories that hold 280,000 words to strategic minds that see five moves ahead, these players have pushed the game beyond what most thought possible. This is the story of the greatest players to ever place tiles on a board.</p>

